highlights.text: “Vem Vem” by Jmilton and MC Xangai is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Taiwan, up 11 spots at #69.
“看着我的眼睛说” by 张远 has been on Viral Songs Taiwan the longest, at 79 days straight.
Go Shiina	 has the most spots on Viral Songs Taiwan. “竈門炭治郎のうた -OST ver.-” is the highest at #7.
“维密秀” by 泰格西, Lil Asian, and Yung Fazo is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Taiwan at #51.
